description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic, self-motivated and experienced team member support the planning and production of clinical rotas to meet the requirements of the Medical Directorate based across Cardiff and Vale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will look forward to a challenging and rewarding work environment, where initiative and team working play a key part.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The primary responsibilities of the role are to assist the Clinical Workforce Hub Coordinators and Management team in the delivery of all Clinical staff rota activity, along with the accurate completion of pay cards for all staff within the scope of the Clinical Workforce Hub.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Clinical Workforce Support Assistant is a point of contact for basic Clinical rota queries and maintains contact with Resources’ Manager and wider Clinical Workforce Resource Team to ensure the team is able to manage, coordinate and report on staff availability, short notice absence and appropriate skill mix sets in a timely manner.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Clinical Workforce Support Assistant is required to demonstrate a high level of discretion the handling of confidential staff information.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder is required to work on a rotational basis to meet the operating hours of the department across a seven-day working week. We are searching for an individual who is able to demonstrate the core values of Cardiff and Vale University Health Board:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- We care about the people we serve and the people we work with&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- We trust one another&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- We respect each other&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- We take personal responsibility&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- We treat people with kindness&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- We act with integrity&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing Date: 11/11/2020 &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Rhiannon Owen&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Lead Coordinator&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: Rhiannon.Owen4@wales.nhs.uk &lt;/p&gt;
